Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is locked! Why is the door locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we prisoners or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahjumma, just hit me instead like earlier. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Episode 4{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for many reasons. You even got hit because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is severely wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Different than her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she gave us blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Are you really going to sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we say, my mom will never open the door for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Tak! Chief Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a door there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked... That one might be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get out from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should I dig a tunnel with a spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I should! Just go over there, you're disrupting me.{\b1}-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,About the baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You had the chance to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wanted to tell you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a "seaweed ear," would you like some?{\b1}(part of the seaweed at the root that's not common)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"A seaweed ear?" Why is there an ear on seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had anything to eat yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually people get angrier when they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little to get rid of your hunger for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, forget it. How can I eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even so... I can't ignore your sincerity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of taste is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, in this country village there isn't any...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's edible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm eating it because it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm forcibly eating it to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to live a long, long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, you're not a picky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be picky about everything since you're from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right. It's not like I'm Tarzan of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In this sort of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating this sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to live a long life. Ugh, it tastes so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a cochlea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a fish eyeball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really chewy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I pull out the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,hates skipping meals the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can drop off food, {\b1}(something done in prison)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,at least make some rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't die from skipping one meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the storage room is full of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lock me in with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, do you like our Mi Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'd rather prefer the oldest sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that... it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, you frustrating fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to lock them up together so they can either become attached or detached,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a decision will be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at him from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he hates her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really. This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone would like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably couldn't even give it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish Box? What's a Wish Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, give it!{\b1} -Wait, wait. Let me read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's really not interesting, I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He really can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me read it to see how amazing it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I hope my friend can{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}return the stuff she borrowed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you ask your friend to give back the things she borrowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your friend have something on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she couldn't give it back because she lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't put her in a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} If I do an errand, I wish my friends would{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tell me "thank you," even just once.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have some sort of trauma when you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a serious disease, a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you they were boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One more. Last, last. Last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I hope Dad{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} went somewhere nice in Heaven.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When did your father pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to go out on boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed him so I put this in the Wish Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're similar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young, my father
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and mother also passed away from a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's only right that I go to the hospital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um... {\b1}-You already have a girlfriend that you want to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Realistically, we won't be able to raise this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I raise him on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,even after you two are married,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you will still be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This baby will become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a burden to you and your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to give the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a life without blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young... {\b1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my mistake for going to the wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, let's go to the hospital together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to take responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still don't want to let a girl go through something so hard alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.{\b1}-Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And... don't refuse, because I'm going to go to the hospital with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. {\b1}-Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I think it is really fascinating that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we've met 4 times, and we've slept together 2 of the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That connection between people is really{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hard to understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we met in a good situation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess we would call it {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destiny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ Even a bad fate may turn to love. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ Shout and call out.♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ I only love you.♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ My heart wants you, you who is like fate. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ I love you. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquitoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill all of you! All the mosquitoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to the hospital.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't have to worry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will cheer up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to wake you up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... where is the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstetrics, obstetrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about obstetrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl! These two were playing with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she is going to get an abortion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen if we go after her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to break her legs if something were to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So where is this? Quickly! Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think the first ship has already left. What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? We have to make a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? There is nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she answering the call or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young isn't picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be causing trouble for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going to have to make a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship, ship, ship, ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Isn't that President Choi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We are coming, we are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is working without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, coming, just wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obstetrics{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it done yet? How much longer do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on a rotation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Give me a notice when it is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you. What did you come here for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that, that surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the person from the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, how are we going to find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that there are three hospitals here in total, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One on the three way road, one next to the market, and one downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to break into groups to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young's mother with the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you two, since you guys are always scheming things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamo-hamo~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go from the farthest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone finds her, call everyone, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see you, I tell you horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I did was listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who is going through a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But how come you are here, Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the person I wanted to meet is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is more nerve wracking than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You look nice even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to cheer you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is nothing I can tell you except for you to rethink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is something you can't have back even if you regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pray with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I get confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying is all about the heart, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just need to talk comfortably, like you talked to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young! Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take pity on{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the baby that met a{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}very, very bad mother.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let it go to a wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For not being able to protect this baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved that I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be nervous and strengthen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ When I open my eyes ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ let me hear it. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ the words of "I love you", my melody. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO! CEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young. Kim Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm looking for a patient named Kim Mi Young. She has big eyes and pale skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking for her so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to have the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, a girl shouldn't come to a place like this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? It hurt a lot, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, okay? {\b1} -You're really sorry? We're really over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've found her. Kim Mi Young is in consultation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to relax. I will take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to see it well because it's still early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the baby right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it right now, the baby is about 0.2 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,0.2...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,0.2 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much smaller than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fetus can understand everything the parents say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Mother and Child's Health Act, Article 14,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you and the baby's father are allowing me to conduct an induced abortion operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as you were impregnated while you were unconscious due to alcohol or sleeping medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a consent form for the surgery. You just have to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a life form of its own.{\b1\i1}This child will become{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:24:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a burden to you and your future wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got fingers and toes. He's got everything.{\b1\i1}To the baby,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to give him a life without blessings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.62,0:24:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, peekaboo. Peakboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.23,0:24:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you going?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.09,0:25:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry and relax. I'm going to put you{\b1} under general anesthesia now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't! Kim Mi Young, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.12,0:25:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Hurry and take this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.37,0:25:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.27,0:26:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.48,0:26:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After hearing the heartbeat, 9 out of 10 can't go through with the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.22,0:26:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.48,0:26:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.90,0:26:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.05,0:26:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.33,0:26:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Do you know what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.03,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah wait. Let's talk about this. Do you know how tough it was for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.91,0:26:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this something we can solve by talking?{\b1} What happened? What about the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.01,0:26:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You! How could you not even stop her? Do you still call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.99,0:27:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah really!{\b1}- Oh, it's the Chairwoman's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.39,0:27:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the Chairwoman's car!{\b1}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.72,0:27:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how cruel you are! You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.77,0:27:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.23,0:27:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This grandma of yours... My neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.82,0:27:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, listen to me first, please! Everyone, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma! Mi Young's mother!{\b1} -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby... The baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.07,0:27:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is fine. It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.20,0:27:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby is alright.{\b1}- Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Kim Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.40,0:28:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made a selfish decision. I hope you will agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.61,0:28:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.04,0:28:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.19,0:28:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? "I will," what? Tell us what you are thinking comfortably as if you are at home. "I will," what? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.16,0:28:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairwoman, Chairwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.69,0:28:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aigoo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.67,0:28:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, you will marry our Mi Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.49,0:28:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that..!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.74,0:28:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it become that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that I will have the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.59,0:28:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything regarding Kim Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.94,0:28:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I can't marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.59,0:28:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You won't marry her but you want the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.56,0:29:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see our Mi Young as nothing but a surrogate mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.38,0:29:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your words are rather harsh. What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.36,0:29:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After she gives birth to the baby, I will guarantee a new start to her life with exceptional treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.12,0:29:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Tak. Ah, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.57,0:29:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, what a shameless punk. You want her to be a surrogate...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.78,0:29:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiyoo. We don't think of you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.23,0:29:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In my eyes, you're our in-laws and Mi Young is my granddaughter-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.74,0:29:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see the baby as my great-grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.43,0:29:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided. I will definitely get them married.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.23,0:29:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you think. I heard the blabber that he said, but
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.98,0:29:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you must have something in mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.26,0:29:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I think it's practically impossible for us to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.84,0:30:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What..? Are you in your right mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.34,0:30:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We conceived this baby by mistake, not out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage should happen out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what I'm trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.43,0:30:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.55,0:30:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Shut up! How dare you..{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.80,0:30:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.70,0:30:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to say here, especially when the person involved is coming out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.47,0:30:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,End of discussion. Take your irresponsible grandson and leave from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.10,0:30:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will deal with my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.70,0:30:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, aigoo, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.58,0:30:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young is now my granddaughter-in-law, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Hold on! Sister-in law...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.85,0:30:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,just say you'll get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.95,0:30:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, Chairwoman...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.27,0:30:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't my sister-in-law marry your grandson, and we'll become in-laws afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.74,0:31:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you cut our factory some slack?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.19,0:31:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll starve to death without the soap factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.68,0:31:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young, please save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mi Young, we beg of you. You just need to make up your mind.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.27,0:31:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! What kind of embarrassment is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.25,0:31:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we sold our factory and land, we have never sold our souls before!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.54,0:31:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand still if you try to cling onto them one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.36,0:31:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,President Park, you have a boat at least, so you have something to lean on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.78,0:31:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have nothing if we lose the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.34,0:31:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mi Young, please think this through.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.34,0:31:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Our lives are in your hands.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.03,0:31:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I told you to stop! {\i} Are you not listening to me, now that the factory is bankrupt?! Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you like this so suddenly, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.44,0:31:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We should at least hold on to our pride to live!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.81,0:31:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} What are you guys doing with my daughter?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.36,0:31:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She, as you can see, is not pretty nor does she have a great body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.26,0:31:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, was she smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.08,0:32:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she did poorly in school as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.14,0:32:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, why are you saying such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.07,0:32:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always last in math, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.59,0:32:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's lacking in so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.36,0:32:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,instead she is also a child that can never be calculative in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.44,0:32:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though her room is a mess because she can't throw things away (sentimental),
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.35,0:32:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,instead she can't also ever throw away (ignore) a person's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she doesn't listen to her mother when I tell her countless times to please live more shrewdly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.00,0:32:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she's a child that can never refuse the request of a complete stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.52,0:32:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...to our Mi Young, who is like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.02,0:32:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,how dare you pressure her like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.25,0:32:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Who are you all?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.12,0:32:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to tell her what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.30,0:32:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you ask this so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Marriage is like an eternal promise.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.57,0:33:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We don't know each other well enough to make such a commitment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.68,0:33:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we say that we can have the baby, marriage is a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.38,0:33:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you with your senseless talk. Your stomach is so full it's about to burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.70,0:33:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.41,0:33:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One! You are going to have this baby and give it up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.11,0:33:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll become a woman that has a past.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.24,0:34:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Two! You are going to have this baby and raise him/her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.90,0:34:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All you are going to be is a single mom.{\b1\i1} -That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.17,0:34:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.21,0:34:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true but how bewildered must that other person be?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.57,0:34:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's right to force him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.73,0:34:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.65,0:34:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.64,0:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that he pulled you out of the operating room?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.66,0:34:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, he has some conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.03,0:34:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Think through this carefully. It's not like there is no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.39,0:34:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's dad is alive and well. Why in the world would you have this baby as a single mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.31,0:34:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your own selfishness. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.41,0:34:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.71,0:34:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,come see me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.64,0:35:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.60,0:35:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man. I bet he'll be amazing as a husband if they get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.80,0:35:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have no intentions of marrying me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a great person, Gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.32,0:35:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I believe you'd be a great dad to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.61,0:35:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how much you love that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.69,0:35:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go through with this marriage if it's going to make someone unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.88,0:35:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already lost
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.52,0:36:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,my qualification as a man to Se Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.08,0:36:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And although it was our mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.47,0:36:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that the baby in your stomach is our child
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.42,0:36:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,will not ever change.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.19,0:36:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already the bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.20,0:36:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.69,0:36:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a great dad to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.92,0:36:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.11,0:36:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Se Ra is still the only one for me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.70,0:36:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't guarantee how much
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and when my heart will move towards you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.34,0:36:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will promise you this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.63,0:37:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At least to our baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.39,0:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a great dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.86,0:37:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can accept this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.88,0:37:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.01,0:37:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be a great mom to this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.28,0:37:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.58,0:38:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Help out over here, please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.08,0:38:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Hello! {\i} {\b1} Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.15,0:38:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! You look so handsome! {\b1\i1} Come over here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.92,0:38:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always looked like a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.64,0:38:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Please clear this over here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.05,0:38:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook! You're here! Today you went for a red fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.71,0:38:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With the elders of both families...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's done getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.24,0:38:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.70,0:38:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.87,0:38:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.06,0:38:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, getting married today is a little too fast, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.56,0:38:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you want to wait until your belly is as big as a mountain to go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.26,0:39:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know buying things together as newlyweds and going on a honeymoon is part of the fun in getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.85,0:39:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but what can you do? What's done is already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.42,0:39:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They can have the baby, we can reserve a banquet hall
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.14,0:39:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a stunning wedding one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.52,0:39:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt bad that I wasn't able to prepare a dowry because it was so last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.62,0:39:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we prepare everything then, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.03,0:39:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What dowry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.00,0:39:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The best dowry has already been prepared right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.96,0:39:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.96,0:39:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} My Gun.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.70,0:40:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.61,0:40:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.98,0:40:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Gun? It's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.95,0:40:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.41,0:40:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Don't hang up, you can't hang up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.47,0:40:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra! Where are you going? We're going to start soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Se Ra..{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.97,0:40:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.24,0:40:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have something to say to you..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.54,0:40:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you know how long I've been waiting for you to call?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.44,0:40:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how painful it was to wait like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.87,0:40:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.73,0:40:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wronged you greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.09,0:40:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you've wronged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.84,0:40:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, as a human being you've made me wait too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.71,0:40:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you had every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.88,0:41:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't do this again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.75,0:41:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the proposal turning out like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.89,0:41:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.10,0:41:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.60,0:41:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even more sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.60,0:41:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're calling it even, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.81,0:41:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting this go completely, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.16,0:41:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There's no one but you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.04,0:41:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You called exactly at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.30,0:41:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.69,0:41:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like someone's looking for you. Is something going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.18,0:41:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's my first performance as the prima ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.35,0:41:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The first day I stand on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.02,0:41:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} To be honest, I was a bit worried I might mess up because I was so nervous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.76,0:41:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I've heard your voice, I think I can do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.58,0:41:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.86,0:42:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Se Ra, there's no time. Everyone's waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.84,0:42:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun, thank you for calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.70,0:42:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.31,0:42:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.50,0:42:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Here comes the groom!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.08,0:42:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.40,0:42:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's handsome!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.18,0:42:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Brother-in-law! You look so handsome!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.22,0:42:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Brother-in-law!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.31,0:42:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's really handsome.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.09,0:42:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Here comes the bride!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.22,0:43:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty! Wow!{\b1\i1} She's so pretty!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.55,0:43:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's beautiful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.59,0:43:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a goddess!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.27,0:43:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Cute! You're really pretty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.36,0:43:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Beautiful!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.66,0:43:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Now, the bride and groom will exchange their vows.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.78,0:43:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you the bride, Kim Mi Young,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.54,0:43:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}promise to take Lee Gun as your lawfully wedded husband,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.56,0:43:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through happiness, sickness, and loneliness,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.03,0:43:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and to love him unconditionally{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.57,0:43:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} without change?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.38,0:43:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.23,0:44:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you, husband, Lee Gun, promise this as well?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.97,0:44:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.04,0:44:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come now, come now...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.27,0:44:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.70,0:44:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.13,0:44:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's answered 'Yes', everyone you've heard his answer!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.40,0:44:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.05,0:44:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.02,0:44:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there will be the exchange of the rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.28,0:44:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what your father wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.03,0:44:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I had no idea you'd be my life.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.41,0:44:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ For when I looked into your eyes, I knew someday you'd be my wife.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.98,0:45:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I know there's times when I am wrong.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.54,0:45:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.45,0:45:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Ring! {\b1} - I did well, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.63,0:45:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} This is a proposal ring!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.37,0:45:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} It can't be worn by another woman first! It'll bring bad luck!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.09,0:45:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ You took my heart so unexpectedly.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.90,0:45:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause! {\b1}♬ I knew that you would be the one.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.78,0:45:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I always knew that there was something special about you♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.04,0:45:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ the day that you walked into my life.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.95,0:45:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay here for a couple of nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.35,0:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of all the company matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.92,0:46:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Take him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.75,0:46:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he runs a small corner store. He's in charge of a huge enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.76,0:46:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that much. It was an unexpected marriage, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.37,0:46:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Son-in-law Lee,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.53,0:46:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what'll happen if you wrong our Mi Young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.34,0:46:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be the rice scoop, but a baseball bat that'll fly your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.53,0:46:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.03,0:46:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my granddaughter-in-law, you stay here with your mom for a couple of days before you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.38,0:46:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom must be sad to send off her youngest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.82,0:46:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prepare a beautiful newlywed's room in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.69,0:46:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's alright, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.79,0:46:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, then I will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.18,0:46:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay~
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.07,0:46:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.04,0:46:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Have a safe trip back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.58,0:47:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.60,0:47:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.00,0:47:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} CEO!!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.81,0:47:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Oh my.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.93,0:47:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, aigoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.24,0:47:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.18,0:47:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, I'm really thankful that you have accepted all the factory workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.26,0:47:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so I prepared this amazing gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.70,0:47:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the men in your family
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.07,0:47:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are lacking a bit in stamina. So, that's why you're the 9th generation of the only sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.68,0:47:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of nonsense are you spouting?! Our family is not just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.52,0:47:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're above normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.11,0:47:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then from now on, you will be above normal and become the greatest in Korea!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.13,0:47:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.92,0:47:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.41,0:47:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it when you get to Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.15,0:47:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to brag or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.66,0:47:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm the best contributor to this wedding, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.33,0:48:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our island's finest selection at the same level as our famous soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.06,0:48:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have developed this ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.25,0:48:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is what brought
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.33,0:48:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you and our sister-in-law together. {\b1} - Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.17,0:48:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anymore. Hurry and get on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.49,0:48:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairwoman is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.30,0:48:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Chief Secretary Tak? Not taking care of his CEO...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.07,0:48:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.59,0:48:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew the sea that you look upon from a dock would look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.16,0:48:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything with the word "Jang" added to it is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.44,0:48:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Station (like a bus station), airport, dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.56,0:48:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.41,0:48:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook, I don't know when it'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.78,0:48:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but be well until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.01,0:48:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Chief Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.81,0:48:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.93,0:48:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Chief Secretary Tak!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.02,0:48:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chief Secretary, yes! (I hear you calling my name)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.36,0:49:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.59,0:49:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.31,0:49:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold it. She wants us to say our goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.41,0:49:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.04,0:49:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.44,0:49:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.62,0:49:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well, Mi Sook!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.98,0:49:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother-in-law! Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.09,0:49:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.09,0:49:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.74,0:49:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Kim Hee Won{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.88,0:49:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your name was Kim Mi Young when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.81,0:49:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember that clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.14,0:49:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My older brother used to call out, "Mi Young, Mi Young."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.55,0:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, by any chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.84,0:49:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,remember this photo? It was at the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.25,0:50:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell from this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.55,0:50:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a memory of going to the zoo with my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you have a scar from a fire, is it ok for me to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.23,0:50:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how you got the scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.67,0:50:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I think it was when I was 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.09,0:50:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The kettle on the heater in the orphanage fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.84,0:50:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister got the scar when she was 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.19,0:50:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you were my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.68,0:50:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oppa...{\b1}- Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.45,0:50:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How is our baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.10,0:50:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.69,0:51:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For not being able to protect this baby,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.51,0:51:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really, really sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.27,0:51:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.94,0:51:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, I can see a star, Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.69,0:51:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife is looking at you from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.85,0:51:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.69,0:51:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.{\b1}- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.17,0:51:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.{\b1}- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.52,0:51:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.56,0:51:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because it wasn't Miss Se Ra but Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.76,0:51:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.54,0:52:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that the CEO who is 9th generation's only son,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.29,0:52:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,got not only a wife, but a child, like a 1+1 deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.72,0:52:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.44,0:52:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.37,0:52:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma is happy, and Mi Young's mother is happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.37,0:52:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak is happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.35,0:52:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.91,0:52:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can only laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.95,0:52:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Only laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.83,0:52:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, but... (suddenly speaking in lower terms)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.04,0:52:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "hey".
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.13,0:52:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But what about Mrs. Mi Young attracted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.19,0:52:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She is very different from Miss Se Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.89,0:52:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like a wide variety of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.49,0:53:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak, what do you mean by attracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.53,0:53:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Attracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.15,0:53:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.44,0:53:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to open this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.69,0:53:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,President Park told you to open it when you get to Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.15,0:53:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak can have it. I hate him so much that I can't stand a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.30,0:53:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.50,0:53:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength, strength "Joagra".
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.42,0:53:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.41,0:53:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with one gulp you will become
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.82,0:53:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Superman of the night. {\b1}- Superman!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.79,0:53:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go around Hong Kong 3 times in one night and 24 hours isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.86,0:53:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A super stimulant for
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.66,0:53:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,those who are afraid of the night. {\b1}It says it is a stimulant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.21,0:53:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stimulant?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.41,0:54:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is our Island's specialty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.65,0:54:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We, two, invented it ourselves!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You, and my sister-in-law...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.42,0:54:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't say it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.17,0:54:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drink, Drink!{\b1}- Health tonic, health tonic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.66,0:54:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It stimulates me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.89,0:54:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, good. Cool~ Cool~{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.28,0:54:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.83,0:54:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, I fell asleep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.12,0:54:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice that you came in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.24,0:54:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was because, because, of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.94,0:54:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, because of those islanders, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.91,0:54:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got in this mess? {\b1}- CEO, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.33,0:55:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this, this, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.60,0:55:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in their trap, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.06,0:55:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it even make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.40,0:55:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Act all innocent in the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.52,0:55:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the back, cheat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.63,0:55:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.24,0:55:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.96,0:55:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to forgive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.88,0:55:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.78,0:55:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.76,0:55:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.12,0:55:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I came here to escort you.{\b1}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.23,0:55:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's ok. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.90,0:55:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.86,0:55:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you have to be used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.55,0:55:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.15,0:55:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.70,0:56:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the restaurant doing fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.50,0:56:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, of course.{\b1}- And is Miss Mi Sook doing well, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.23,0:56:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, yes.{\b1}- Get in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.58,0:56:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, get in,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.42,0:56:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.53,0:56:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.73,0:56:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The CEO is really busy today, so he couldn't come. {\b1}Continue on getting in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.11,0:56:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.02,0:56:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was all my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.26,0:56:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"It happened because of my mistake. That's right."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.42,0:56:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I should take responsibility."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.83,0:56:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.64,0:56:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been unfairly cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.97,0:56:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for that medicine, if only not for that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.90,0:56:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe she might be part of the plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.77,0:56:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be on the same team, same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.98,0:57:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Same team, same team.{\b1}- You want to vent your anger on anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.42,0:57:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you feel like you will explode right away if anyone touches you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.10,0:57:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.28,0:57:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If I drink like a mad man
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.77,0:57:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I work out 'till I feel like dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.05,0:57:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I sleep like a dead man, but after exactly 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.97,0:57:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,my eyes open and
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.94,0:57:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.76,0:57:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hurts so much and the first thing that comes to my mind is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.57,0:57:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"I got married!"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.66,0:57:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"I got married"...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.79,0:57:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.13,0:57:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.59,0:57:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing that makes me so mad is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.83,0:57:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.01,0:57:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to live my married life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.01,0:57:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with that snail woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.06,0:57:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean by "snail"?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.77,0:57:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean the Mud Snail Bride (from Korean folk tale)?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.85,0:58:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, no not something good like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.84,0:58:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is about a terrifying snail that lives in Yeoul Island.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.97,0:58:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.48,0:58:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are scared of snails? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.32,0:58:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about snails is that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.07,0:58:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they look innocent from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.33,0:58:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but their suction force is so strong. It's just incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.68,0:58:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get sucked by a snail,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.40,0:58:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that terrifying sucking feet,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.26,0:58:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}slowly, little-by-little, piece-by-piece,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.59,0:58:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a giant house on its back,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.60,0:58:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}toward the target,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.89,0:58:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}slowly, little-by-little, piece-by-piece, getting closer..{\i}
